title: TUESDAY - MNF Recap
itunes:title: TUESDAY - MNF Recap
description:
Week 6 of the NFL season is in the books as Kyler Murray (0:15) has quite the homecoming in Texas as the Cardinals head to Big D and take care of the Cowboys. In the other matchup (0:32) it was Chiefs, once again, showing they are the class of the AFC with the win over the Bills. Speaking of the Bills, Good Morning Football's Peter Schrager (1:45) gets into it if Buffalo was crowned a little too early. We have all the latest injury news from around the league (2:54) as well, including the latest woes for the Eagles offense (3:30)
